snippet: Ireland's former Olympic chief Pat Hickey returned to Dublin on Sunday and said he will continue to fight to clear his name after being charged in Brazil in August over an alleged scheme to sell Olympic tickets illegally....
lead_paragraph: Ireland's former Olympic chief Pat Hickey returned to Dublin on Sunday and said he will continue to fight to clear his name after being charged in Brazil in August over an alleged scheme to sell Olympic tickets illegally.

headline.main: Olympics: Hickey Returns to Ireland, Vows to Clear Name
headline.print_headline: Olympics: Hickey Returns to Ireland, Vows to Clear Name
